The '''Lesser Fanatic''' (named '''Jeffery''') is located in [[Edgeville]], by the bridge. He awards players the [[Wilderness sword]] for completing the easy, medium, hard and elite tasks of the [[Wilderness Diary]].

He is accompanied by [[Luna]], a [[rabbit]].
